information. Information about ads served, viewed, or clicked on, such as the
type of ad, where the ad was served, whether you clicked on it, the number of
times you have seen the ad, the number of Vungle ads viewed per session, and
whether you visited the Advertiser’s website or relevant app store and/or
purchased or installed the product or service advertised.
